de.mrapp.android.dialog.adapter

Class ArrayAdapter<Type>

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.widget.BaseAdapter
      • android.widget.ArrayAdapter<Type>
        • de.mrapp.android.dialog.adapter.ArrayAdapter<Type>
  • Type Parameters:
    Type - The type of the adapter's underlying data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.widget.Adapter, android.widget.Filterable, android.widget.ListAdapter, android.widget.SpinnerAdapter

    public class ArrayAdapter<Type>
extends android.widget.ArrayAdapter<Type>
    An adapter, which is extended from the class ArrayAdapter in order to be able to customize the text and control color of the adapter's items.
    Since:
    1.2.0
    Author:
    Michael Rapp
